7-04-03T03:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>覺 所以冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n由其女仔圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  假到乜咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我ex既朋友圈真係復雜到咁仆街（得佢天真到相信人係真心對佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但事實上個個都係到當佢傻仔咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n睇下ex幾時會仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n申利：ex 係女"},{"pid":"4691648c4c193b6efcde5f1a818201e8ab315216","tid":184633,"uid":101997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:10:23.000Z","msg":"覺呀<br />\n雖然去到每個環境都會識好多人<br />\n有飯腳、會有幾句嘢傾咁<br />\n但其實無乜共同興趣又唔算太熟<br />\n放假或者畢咗業之後其實都無乜聯絡<br />\n其實真係無乜真心朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695e704e077790f16c0c3b0a449e4f382492441b","tid":184633,"uid":100861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:11:12.000Z","msg":"剛出黎社會？"}]}